mean_cn: adj. 不兼容的，矛盾的，不调和的
mean_en: two actions, ideas, etc. that are incompatible are not acceptable or possible together because of basic differences; two people who are incompatible are very different from each other and so are not able to live or work happily together; two things that are incompatible are of different types so that they cannot be used or mixed together
sentence: This is incompatible with that - they won't work together.
sentence_trans: 这两个是不兼容的，它们凑不到一起。
word_etyma: in不，非 + compat兼容 + ible……的 → incompatible不兼容的，矛盾的，不调和的
